                    gemeinsam helfen<br />zur richtigen Zeit<br />am richtigen Ort
                </h1>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="ui basic vertical segment">
        <div class="ui one column centered stackable grid container">
            <div class="nine wide center aligned column">
